import React from "react";
import { FacebookIcon } from "@material-ui/icons/Facebook";
import TwitterIcon from '@material-ui/icons/Twitter'
import InstagramIcon from '@material-ui/icons/Instagram';  

import {
  SocialIconLink,
  SocialIcons,
  SocialLogo,
  SocialMedia,
  SocialMediaWrap,
  WebsiteRights,
  FooterLinksContainer,
  FooterLinksWrapper,
  FooterLinksItems,
  FooterLink,
  SocialIcon,
} from "./FooterElements";

const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <FooterLinksContainer>
      <FooterLinksWrapper>
        <FooterLinksItems>
          <FooterLink to="/faq">Account and Billing</FooterLink>
          <FooterLink to="/faq">Plans and Pricing</FooterLink>
        </FooterLinksItems>
        <FooterLinksItems>
          <FooterLink to="/faq">FAQ</FooterLink>
          <FooterLink to="/faq">Help Center</FooterLink>
        </FooterLinksItems>
        <FooterLinksItems>
          <FooterLink to="/faq">Privacy</FooterLink>
          <FooterLink to="/faq">Terms of Use</FooterLink>
        </FooterLinksItems>
      </FooterLinksWrapper>
      <SocialMedia>
        <SocialMediaWrap>
          <SocialLogo to="/">
            <SocialIcon />
            MOVIEFLIX
          </SocialLogo>
          <WebsiteRights>MOVIEFLIX Â© 2020</WebsiteRights>
          <SocialIcons>
            <SocialIconLink href="/" target="_blank" aria-label="Facebook">
              <FacebookIcon />
            </SocialIconLink>
            <SocialIconLink href="/" target="_blank" aria-label="Twitter">
              <TwitterIcon />
            </SocialIconLink>
            <SocialIconLink href="/" target="_blank" aria-label="Youtube">
              <FaYoutube />
            </SocialIconLink>
            <SocialIconLink href="/" target="_blank" aria-label="Instagram">
              <InstagramInst />
            </SocialIconLink>
          </SocialIcons>
        </SocialMediaWrap>
      </SocialMedia>
    </FooterLinksContainer>
  );
};

export default Footer;
